---
title: Seared Pork Sandos with Tangy Apple Slaw Elevated Dinners, Impressively Easy
description: Pork and apples are a match made in heaven. You’ll pile a mustardy apple-cabbage slaw atop seared boneless pork chops on pillowy toasted brioche buns. Serve with a bright, peppery arugula salad tossed in a honey-Dijon dressing and sprinkled with croutons for crunchy contrast to round out this hearty 15-minute meal.

